Enum GlideExecutor.UncaughtThrowableStrategy

  • java.lang.Object

    GlideExecutor

    public static enum GlideExecutor.UncaughtThrowableStrategy
extends Enum<GlideExecutor.UncaughtThrowableStrategy>
    A strategy for handling unexpected and uncaught Throwables thrown by futures run on the pool.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      IGNORE
      Silently catches and ignores the uncaught Throwables.
      LOG
      Logs the uncaught Throwables using GlideExecutor.TAG and Log.
      THROW
      Rethrows the uncaught Throwables to crash the app.

    • Field Summary

      static GlideExecutor.UncaughtThrowableStrategy DEFAULT
      The default strategy, currently LOG.
